data.text:
2012-13

55 Meter Hurdles:

 Finished in 18th place with a personal-best of 7.97at the Red Raider Open

60 meter Hurdles:

 Clocked a lifetime-best of 8.53 at the Howie Ryan. Invitational

 Had four top-20 finishes.

110 Meter Hurdles:

 Ran a personal-best at the Sun Belt Conference Outdoor Championships (14.94)

 Grabbed three top-five finishes during the outdoor season.

400 Meter Hurdles:

 Ran to a seventh-place finish at the SBC Outdoor Championships, where he posted a lifetime-best of 53.28

 Was the event winner at the North Texas Classic.

Relays:

 Was a member of the 4X400M relay in both indoor and outdoor

 Placed third at the TCU Invitational.

2011-12

110 Meter Hurdles:

 Ran a season-best 15.39 110 hurdles at the UTA Bobby Lane Invitational.

Relays:

 Was a leg of the 4x100 meter relay team that took first at the SBC Outdoor Championships

 Was a member of the 4x400 meter relay team that finished second at the SBC Outdoor Championships.

2010-11

 Finished fifth in the 60 meter hurdles at the Sooner Invitational in 8.57

 Participated in two meets during the outdoor season, the UTA Bobby Lane Invite and the Michael Johnson Classic.

High School/Personal

 Was a District 8-4A runner-up and regional qualifier in the 300 hurdles in 2009

 Qualified for the 4A State Championship as a member of the 4x400 relay.
